{"tid":1718941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"依家我哋面臨嘅問題係形象嘅問題","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T04:10:21.000Z","uid":64810,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8accf8ff05b6107d7d68d83b4a303f15b8708c61","tid":1718941,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:28:16.000Z","msg":"我分幾點講<span style=\"color: red;\">想睇重點嘅就睇紅字</span><br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">咪作假新聞 相信前線手足</span><br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">掃走主面上既左報 減少洗腦 特別東方</span> 要教育佢地唔好人講就信 我知好難 但依家係假新聞最多既階段<br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重欠缺文文宣 出師無名 要將社會現象歸咎政府</span> ：琴日曉打講既 政府若果好 社會就唔會咁 、運動已經持續左五個啦 政府完全無誠意解決問題 縱容警暴導致  <span style=\"color: red;\">切記我地都要拉一派打一派 政府拉緊港豬入藍 我地唔止要拉攏返佢地變黃 仲要拉埋內地人落如果做到既話</span><br />\n<br />\n4<span style=\"color: red;\">海外報導開始唔幫示威者 我地要加強海外文宣 / Twitter </span><br />\n<br />\n5<span style=\"color: red;\">形象塑造要加強</span> 近日實在太撚多暴力畫面 中共喉舌有大量彈藥（唔該你地記得black boc..) <span style=\"color: red;\">我地需要有和平既集會/咩都好 去挽回自己嘅形象呢點好撚重要</span> 美國副總統已經講到明。經過4日既黎明行動 我地好撚成功但美圖白宮對CU單嘢無出過聲 我唔知係中美貿易定點 定係我地既形象既問題 <span style=\"color: red;\">但切記我地都需要和善既形象 <br />\n今晚有支持消防員既集會 去唔到愛丁堡既人 不如喺同一時間係自己區內搞集會</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黎明行動一定要繼續 繼續表達五大訴求當訴求完成個陣自然社會會回復 要直接將民憤拉返去政府嗰邊將個波拋番比無能嘅政府。</span><br />\n<br />\n琴日已經有3個手足出左事啦 一個仲死左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好麻木 我地輸左後係無未來 無一世 <br />\nStay strong.</span>"},{"pid":"f09e0fc8736b020d7ef70732d093f79625020c6a","tid":1718941,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7de7b586418b399b04e4375e0e29e8659a32a3","tid":1718941,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38636e78e7ed437e45d98703ac55ce50f4b2fc8b","tid":1718941,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0600ab08c05d11e1d3676ea2d0e5dabd9be965","tid":1718941,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb7c24280dbb8e7aa729d80462589b4106d87f1","tid":1718941,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40730744febf434cb6f16ec0def7c6934ccfd844","tid":1718941,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dcd1e54517dfdb6420c8bac1801a067c57bc74","tid":1718941,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score